snippet.title: MeiQ: Labyrinth of Death Opening Movie
snippet.description:
GAME: http://bit.ly/meiqGS
Amazon UK: http://bit.ly/meiq_amz

Join your robot Guardian and fight through four towers in this dungeon-crawling RPG to restore the world's light! With endless parts customization, elemental affinities, and unique partner-based battles, your experience is as deep as the labyrinths!
